content.problemStatement:
What will be the output of the following Java code snippet.

```java
class Seedit {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int row = 4;

        while (row >= 1) {
            int col = 1;
            while (col <= row) {
                System.out.print("* ");
                col++;
            }
            System.out.println();
            row--;
        }
    }
}
```

